title: Hour 1 - Reggie Miller (07-30-20)
itunes:title: Hour 1 - Reggie Miller (07-30-20)
description:
Reggie Miller tells Dan about his life in the bubble. Reggie says the key is to watch the officials. Reggie says the fans can some times sway a refs next calls; so with no fans in the stands; this will make the officials the real key.
